  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how the, the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] movement started to, to, to, to extract us out of the ghetto into the, into the, into the wagons on our way to the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- this was a process-- this was a process of--- you know, this was a process that took almost four years.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'd like to go back, still earlier, and talk a little bit more about some of the earlier things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you have to move into the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we already lived-- the ghetto in, in, in Lodz was a Jewish-- there was a Jewish quarters, and some Jews lived outside of those quarters.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I say quarters, I mean, it's like in-- possibly in the olden days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and as you came into this country, you had the Irish communities that sort of gathered there, and the Yiddish, and the Italians, and Greeks, and so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you're comfortable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to this day, we still have those communities, and so there was the Jewish quarters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- in, in, in Lodz, in that particular time, where we lived was the Jewish quarters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this is how they took it geographically, saying well, since we have the majority of the Jews in this part of the area anyway, this is where we're going to form the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those that were outside that perimeter would then be transported into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- and then wire off the ghetto and enclose the ghetto, so to speak, which they did with the-- with the fences and the bridges.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
